videos.author: MTGGoldfish
videos.title: Red Has a Sheoldred for Two Mana!?  Duskmourn Standard
videos.description:
Razorkin Needlhead is pretty much a mini Sheoldred and red has a ton of ways to deal damage to the face with burn thanks to Duskmourn! Throw that all together with Ojer Axonil and Solphim and a lot of damage is going to be flying around!

Today's video is brought to you by Card Kingdom. You can pick up some Magic: the Gathering cards (and help support the show) at https://www.cardkingdom.com/mtggoldfish
